Collections.rule:
Individual: @B*
Types: Player
Facts: name @B*(xsd:string)
Facts: country @D*
Facts: playerId @E*(xsd:long)

Individual: @B*(rdf:ID=(@N*, "-", @D*))
Types: MatchMap
Facts: map @D*
Facts: match @N*
Facts: team1rounds @E*(xsd:integer)
Facts: team2rounds @F*(xsd:integer)

Individual: @B*(rdf:ID=(@F*, "-", @E*, "matchPlayer"))
Types: MatchPlayer
Facts: team @C*
Facts: match @F*
Facts: kills @G*(xsd:integer)
Facts: assists @H*(xsd:integer)
Facts: deaths @I*(xsd:integer)
Facts: hs @J*(xsd:integer)
Facts: flashAssists @K*(xsd:integer)
Facts: kast @L*(xsd:float)
Facts: kddiff @M*(xsd:float)
Facts: adr @N*(xsd:float)
Facts: fkdiff @O*(xsd:float)
Facts: rating @P*(xsd:float)
Facts: playerRef @E*
